% LC_NAME: Minimal definition for English business contexts
% Indonesian naming conventions (single names, Javanese/Balinese/Chinese/Arabic
% traditions) don't fully map to Western formats. This provides basic support
% for English formal contexts using Mr./Ms. prefixes while avoiding
% misrepresentation of Indonesian naming patterns.
%
LC_NAME
name_fmt    "%d%t%g%t%m%t%f"
END LC_NAME

